<li>My deepest sympathies on the passing of your dear friend.</li>
<li>Your friendship meant so much to (deceased's name), and to me.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and love during this heartbreaking time.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and remembering the good times with (deceased's name).</li>
<li>I am here for you, whatever you need, anytime.</li>
<li>May fond memories bring you comfort during your grief.</li>
<li>Please know that I am thinking of you and sending my love.</li>
<li>I will always remember (deceased's name)'s kindness and generosity.</li>
<li>Your friend will be deeply missed, but never forgotten.</li>
<li>May peace find you in the midst of your sorrow.</li>
<li>Your friendship is a treasure to cherish, even in this sadness.</li>
<li>I'm here to listen if you need to talk, no pressure at all.</li>
